{{Infobox video game |title = Holiday Island |image = |developer = [[Sunflowers Interactive Entertainment Software]] |publisher = Sunflowers Interactive Entertainment Software |released = 1996 |genre = [[Strategy]] |modes = [[Single-player]] |platform = [[personal computer|PC]] }}
'''''Holiday Island''''' is a [[Business simulation game|business simulation]] [[video game]] developed by German games design company [[Sunflowers Interactive Entertainment Software|Sunflower]]. Much of the game play involves juggling funds to build hotels, accommodation, leisure activities and restaurants. The number and location of these is important, as is the interconnectivity between different facilities. There are also other people like the player constructing and starting businesses in the island. The player can hire a Mafia style hitman to ruin the other people's businesses.
